          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Pitch-Curve</text><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image> is the path, or locus, of the center of a Cam-Follower Roller, relative to the Cam Part, throughout a machine <text style="font-weight:normal;">cycle. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-weight:normal;">When the shape of the Cam-Follower</text><text style="font-weight:bold;">&#32;</text>is not circular, the Pitch-Curve has no meaning. </para>
